data.description:
Please do not disturb the current tenants! 

3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home in the sweet lake community of Silver Shores Estates is just across the street from the lake, neighborhood boat ramp and pier. Energy efficient windows installed in 2020. Wood-look laminate floors are carried throughout the home. Living area has a nice open floor plan. Large ornamental brick fireplace (non wood burning). Family dining area, Functional kitchen with good sized pantry, freshly painted cabinets, new tile floors, fresh countertops, motion censored undermount lights, and a new microwave. Two guest bedrooms, Master Suite, Patio and fire pit in the back yard along with storage shed. The garage door and keypad are wifi operable! RV parking, wood privacy fence and sprinkler system.

**Property is currently occupied - please do not disturb current tenants **
